  "texts": [
    "This is notable because GPT-4 is actually the only LLM that performs well with pandas agent, likely because it performs better on the coding tasks that pandas agent orchestrates behind the scenes relative to other LLMs.",
    "Ultimately, GPT-4 is a very comprehensive LLM and performs remarkably well on a wide variety of tasks, even outside standard NLP tasks.",
    "However, other large open sourced LLMs can often outperform GPT-4 with fine-tuning.",
    "Fine-tuning open sourced LLMs to work effectively with pandas agent or even finetuning the Llama-2-70b model without the use of pandas agent may come close to, if not equal, the performance of GPT-4 coupled to pandas agent.",
    "Although our tabular analysis example was demonstrated on a very specific marketing use case, the results should generalize to other rowby-row table summarization tasks."
